data.description: Beautiful, updated 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath Colonial with 2 car garage. This home offers recently installed flooring, lighting, updated kitchen and baths, stainless steel appliance package, gas heat/AC, 2 car garage and private, fenced in yard. A lot of living space for your family, close proximity to schools, beaches, shopping, NJ route 9 and GS Parkway. Come make this your NEW home for the New Year!
